'''Tusnakt''' d tussna ye mḍanen s we mata, tettwa sileγ s ti musniwin ti madwanin (connaissances abstraites) s tallat n [[A zebz|i zebzan]] [[Tameẓla|i meẓlan]] (raisonnements logiques) γef [[ta miḍrant|te miḍranin]] (consepts) aem [[amḍan|ye mḍanen]] (nombres), [[ta nzeggit]] (géométrie), [[ti skiwt (tusnakt)|ti skiwin]] (structures) neγ [[i seγwal i nezgiyen|i seγwal]] (transformation). Tusnakt tbedd daγen γef taγult n [[ta gmi tusnit|te gmi]] (recherche) ig ssendalen (developpe) ti musniwin, akk d w'ayen it sselmad.

== Azar n w'awal ==

Tusnakt d'awal id yussan deg sin w'awalen i lelliyen '''tussna''' d '''kti''' (tussna= science, kti = calculer tusnakt= science de calcul(mathématiques), tussna n we ktay).
Awal n tusnakt d awal a maynut iss nefka deg timidi aki nneɣ, uqbel [[imaziɣen|i maziɣen]] neɣ le qbayel d wid yesseqdacen tusnakt d acu s [[tutlayt|tutlayin]] nniḍen, ama deg tusnakt ama deg [[tussna|tusniwin]] nniḍen, aem [[augustin]]

